SUMMARY:Women’s Evening Bible Study
DESCRIPTION:Women’s Evening Bible Study is back!\nJoin us every Thursday at 5:45 p.m. in Room 213 for a time of fellowship\, learning\, and spiritual growth. \nThis season\, we’ll be studying John—the disciple known for his deep friendship with Jesus and his powerful testimony about the Word. Together\, we’ll explore how John reveals Jesus as the eternal Word made flesh and how this truth shapes our faith\, our identity\, and our daily walk with Christ.\nWhether you’re new or returning\, all are welcome to come as you are and be part of a supportive community. \nFor more information\, please contact Jen Randolph at jen.rn@verizon.net.
URL:https://firstpresevanston.org/event/womens-evening-bible-study-2/
LOCATION:First Presbyterian Evanston\, 1427 Chicago Avenue Evanston\, IL\, 60201\, United States
CATEGORIES:First Presbyterian Events,Small Group
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://firstpresevanston.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ChildrensBible800x600EventTile.jpg
END:VEVENT
