SUMMARY:Sunday Morning Worship
DESCRIPTION:Our worship services are held each Sunday morning at 10:30 a.m.\, with Communion taking place the first Sunday of each month. Join us in person or online. \nThis service will be also streamed live at 10 a.m. Sunday on the First Pres website and at https://live.firstpresevanston.org. \nYou can find the bulletin for this week’s service here. \nCommunion is served on the first Sunday of each month. All who confess Jesus Christ as savior are invited to partake.
