SUMMARY:Half-Day Hooray
DESCRIPTION:Half-Day Hooray!\nNext Event:\n📅 Wednesday\, April 8\n🕐 12:30–4:30 p.m. \nJoin us for an afternoon of fun\, movement\, and connection!\nHalf-Day Hooray (HDH) is designed for kids in grades K–5 and takes place on District 65 half days (first Wednesday of each month). \n\nWhat is Half-Day Hooray?\nHDH provides a safe\, nurturing\, and fun environment where kids can: \n\nMake new friends\nBuild confidence\nExplore faith\n…and parents enjoy a little extra time in their day!\n\nNo prior church experience is needed — everyone is welcome. \n\nWhat’s Included?\n\nLunch: Kid-friendly favorites (chicken nuggets\, pasta\, pizza\, veggies\, fruit\, dessert).\nFood allergies? Contact our Children’s Director for accommodations.\nService Project: Pack care packages\, write letters\, and help others in need.\nMusic & Movement: Songs\, rhythm\, and high-energy activities.\nBible Story Time: Age-appropriate stories about God’s love and kindness.\nCrafts & Creativity: Fun projects to take home.\nGames & Gym Time: Active play to burn off energy!\n\n\nCost & Registration\nTo keep HDH sustainable\, we now charge a small fee with flexible options: \nSingle Session: \n\n$8 per child\n$20 family max per day\n\nSeason Pass (Feb–May): \n\n$30 per child for all 4 sessions\n$50 per family for all 4 sessions\n\n💡 If cost is a concern\, please reach out — we never want finances to prevent participation. \n\nHow to Register & Pay\nRealm: \n\nA Realm login is required. Contact us at 847-864-1472 to request one.\nNew families can create an account easily.\n✅ Click here to register and pay on Realm\n\nZelle: \n\nMemo: Seeds of Faith Fund – HDH 2026\nUse your bank’s app or camera to scan the QR code below.\n\n\n\nQuestions?\nCall us at 847-864-1472 or email the Children’s Director.
URL:https://firstpresevanston.org/event/half-day-hooray-2/
LOCATION:First Presbyterian Evanston\, 1427 Chicago Avenue Evanston\, IL\, 60201\, United States
CATEGORIES:Featured Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://firstpresevanston.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Half_Day_Hooray_LogoV1.png
END:VEVENT
