SUMMARY:Nourish Women's Bible Study
DESCRIPTION:The Nourish Women’s Bible Study will resume their weekly meetings on September 18\, 9:30 a.m. in Room 213. The fall will feature a study/discussion on “Empowered to Share Our Faith.” Come for study\, prayer\, and fellowship. Women of all ages are welcome. Childcare provided upon request. Contact sallyivaska1@gmail.com.
